00:00:31.892 --> 00:00:35.818
What are you cooking today?
Spicy Chick Peas Snack (Masala Senaga Vada)

00:00:40.143 --> 00:00:43.021
Ingredients required to make Masala Senaga Vada

00:00:43.129 --> 00:00:48.689
Chick Peas, Green Gram, White Lentil, Green Chilli, Ginger

00:00:49.015 --> 00:00:55.533
Cinnamon, Coriander Leaves, Mint Leaves, Carrot, Sliced Onions &amp; Oil

00:01:05.284 --> 00:01:32.594
Soak a cup of chick peas, half cup of green gram &amp; half cup of white lentil in water for 4 hours

00:01:52.853 --> 00:02:07.538
Now take all three and grind them along with some green chilli,
cinnamon, ginger, cloves, masala and salt

00:02:19.786 --> 00:02:36.246
Add some coriander, mint, grated carrot and sliced onions into the ground paste

00:02:39.134 --> 00:02:40.851
Mix it all thoroughly

00:02:44.160 --> 00:02:49.804
Take a pan for deep frying and heat some oil

00:03:01.257 --> 00:03:06.935
Chick peas are full of fibre which is very healthy and a perfect snack for kids

00:03:27.205 --> 00:03:32.243
Make small patties with mixed paste

00:03:34.911 --> 00:03:39.301
Now fry them

00:03:53.918 --> 00:03:57.486
Fry till they're golden brown in color

00:04:17.782 --> 00:04:20.575
Garnish with some coriander and carrots

